column2: Core Trust Seal
column13: The repository has an explicit mission to provide access to and preserve data in its domain

column2: Core Trust Seal
column13: The repository maintains all applicable licenses covering data access and use and monitors compliance.

column2: Core Trust Seal
column13: The repository has a continuity plan to ensure ongoing access to and preservation of its holdings.

column2: Core Trust Seal
column13: The repository ensures, to the extent possible, that data are created, curated, accessed, and used in compliance with disciplinary and ethical norms.

column2: Core Trust Seal
column13: The repository has adequate funding and sufficient numbers of qualified staff managed through a clear system of governance to effectively carry out the mission.

column2: Core Trust Seal
column13: The repository adopts mechanism(s) to secure ongoing expert guidance and feedback (either inhouse, or external, including scientific guidance, if relevant).

column2: Core Trust Seal
column13: The repository guarantees the integrity and authenticity of the data.

column2: Core Trust Seal
column13: The repository accepts data and metadata based on defined criteria to ensure relevance and understandability for data users.

column2: Core Trust Seal
column13: The repository applies documented processes and procedures in managing archival storage of the data.

column2: Core Trust Seal
column13: The repository assumes responsibility for long-term preservation and manages this function in a planned and documented way.

column2: Core Trust Seal
column13: The repository has appropriate expertise to address technical data and metadata quality and ensures that sufficient information is available for end users to make quality-related evaluations.

column2: Core Trust Seal
column13: Archiving takes place according to defined workflows from ingest to dissemination.

column2: Core Trust Seal
column13: The repository enables users to discover the data and refer to them in a persistent way through proper citation.

column2: Core Trust Seal
column13: The repository enables reuse of the data over time, ensuring that appropriate metadata are available to support the understanding and use of the data.

column2: Core Trust Seal
column13: The repository functions on well-supported operating systems and other core infrastructural software and is using hardware and software technologies appropriate to the services it provides to its Designated Community.

column2: Core Trust Seal
column13: The technical infrastructure of the repository provides for protection of the facility and its data, products, services, and users.
